<section>
    <h2>Transport Information</h2>
    <h3>Bus and Train Transportation</h3>
    <h4>Directions from Tai Wo MTR:</h4>
    <p>To reach the elderly home, take the following transportation options:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Train:</strong> Take the East Rail Line towards Kowloon, alight at Tai Po Market MTR.</li>
        <li><strong>Bus:</strong> Take Bus 75K from Tai Wo MTR, which goes directly to the elderly home.</li>
    </ul>
    <img src="https://example.com/tai_wo_transport.jpg" alt="Transport directions from Tai Wo MTR">

    <h4>Directions from Tai Po Market MTR:</h4>
    <p>At Tai Po Market MTR, you have the following options:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Train:</strong> East Rail Line towards Lok Ma Chau.</li>
        <li><strong>Bus:</strong> Take Bus 64K from Tai Po Market towards the elderly home.</li>
    </ul>
    <img src="https://example.com/tai_po_transport.jpg" alt="Transport directions from Tai Po Market MTR">

    <h4>Bus Routes:</h4>
    <p>Various bus routes serve the elderly home. Key routes include:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Bus 75K</li>
        <li>Bus 64K</li>
        <li>Bus 80</li>
    </ul>
    <img src="https://example.com/bus_routes.jpg" alt="Bus routes to elderly home">
</section>